/*

Purpose:			Utility to delete a Scan Reader object from real object passed in

Parameters:			_pxyScanReader	CM_ScanReaderObj 	The Scan Reader object to delete
					_passport		CM_Passport			Passport to use for our Trx that holds errors and other useful data

Return Value:		NONE

Date		Who		Reason
03 May 2022	navpw1	Initial creation TFS: 52773

*/

